<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Welcome to CuraKidney</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .logo {
        max-width: 250px;
        height: auto;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666666;
      }
      h1 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #d1243b;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #d1243b;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .highlight {
        color: #d1243b;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .success-icon {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 48px;
        color: #2aaea0;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }
      .divider {
        border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          width: 100%;
        }
        .content {
          padding: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <img
          src='https://curakidney-assets-production.up.railway.app/images/curakidney-logo.png'
          alt='CuraKidney Logo'
          class='logo'
        />
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <div class='success-icon'>✓</div>
        <h1>Welcome to CuraKidney, Dr. Policarpio!</h1>

        <p style='font-size: 16px; color: #333;'><span
            class='highlight'
          >Congratulations!</span>
          Your Nephrologist account has been successfully created.</p>

        <p style='font-size: 15px; color: #444;'>We're thrilled to welcome you
          to the CuraKidney platform, where you can manage patient care, access
          clinical data, and collaborate with your healthcare team seamlessly.</p>

        <p style='font-size: 15px; color: #444;'><strong>Your account is now
            ready to use.</strong>
          Here's how to get started:</p>

        <ul style='font-size: 14px; color: #444;'>
          <li>Log in using your email address and the password you created</li>
          <li>Complete your profile information to personalize your experience</li>
          <li>Review available patient records and upcoming appointments</li>
          <li>Explore our clinical tools and resources designed for
            nephrologists</li>
        </ul>

        <a
          href='{{loginUri}}'
          class='button'
          style='font-size: 14px; display: inline-block; background-color: #d1243b; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold;'
        >
          Log In Now
        </a>

        <div class='divider'></div>

        <p style='color: #444; font-size: 14px;'>Our team has developed
          CuraKidney with the specific needs of nephrology specialists in mind.
          We're confident that our platform will enhance your practice and
          improve patient outcomes.</p>

        <p style='color: #777; font-size: 13px;'>If you have any questions or
          need assistance, our support team is here to help. Contact us at
          <a
            href='mailto:support@curakidney.com'
            style='color: #2AAEA0;'
          >support@curakidney.com</a>
          or call our dedicated provider line at (555) 123-4567.</p>

        <div class='divider'></div>

        <p>We look forward to supporting your practice,</p>
        <p><strong>The CuraKidney Team</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>© 2025 CuraKidney. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
          <a href='#' style='color: #666666;'>Privacy Policy</a>
          |
          <a href='#' style='color: #666666;'>Terms of Service</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>